<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-11-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-11-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="31" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d31">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 863.001F85/8a</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Emperor</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-11-22">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 22, 1916</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>I beg of Your Majesty and the Imperial and Royal Family to accept the
                            sincerest sympathy of Mrs. Wilson and myself in the great loss which you
                            have sustained in the death of your illustrious uncle, for whom I
                            entertained sentiments of high esteem and regard. I also extend to Your
                            Majesty the condolences of the Government and people of the United
                            States, and convey to you my best wishes for your personal well-being
                            and prosperity.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodrow Wilson</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>